{
  "_comment": [
    "ComfyUI workflow: Style-Consistent Enhancement via IP-Adapter + ControlNet",
    "",
    "Used by two modes:",
    "  enhance      — sketch + user's own art → personal style, commercial quality",
    "  style_explore — sketch + any style ref → see sketch in a different art style",
    "",
    "IP-Adapter weight is overwritten at runtime by art_enhancer.py:",
    "  enhance:      0.85  (stay close to style reference)",
    "  style_explore: 0.65 (looser blend with base model)",
    "",
    "Node roles (referenced by ID in art_enhancer.py):",
    "  '2' → LoadImage: sketch input   (overwritten at runtime)",
    "  '3' → LoadImage: style reference (overwritten at runtime)",
    "  '6' → IPAdapterAdvanced: weight  (overwritten at runtime)",
    "",
    "SETUP (one-time):",
    "  1. Install IP-Adapter nodes:",
    "       cd ComfyUI/custom_nodes",
    "       git clone https://github.com/cubiq/ComfyUI_IPAdapter_plus.git",
    "  2. Download IP-Adapter model → ComfyUI/models/ipadapter/",
    "       ip-adapter-plus_sdxl_vit-h.bin",
    "       https://huggingface.co/h94/IP-Adapter/tree/main/sdxl_models",
    "  3. Download CLIP Vision model → ComfyUI/models/clip_vision/",
    "       CLIP-ViT-H-14-laion2B-s32B-b79K.safetensors",
    "       https://huggingface.co/h94/IP-Adapter/tree/main/models/image_encoder",
    "  4. Confirm ckpt_name and control_net_name match your downloaded files.",
    "  5. See doc/art_module_setup.md for full instructions."
  ],
  "1": {
    "class_type": "CheckpointLoaderSimple",
    "inputs": {
      "ckpt_name": "AnythingXL_xl.safetensors"
    }
  },
  "2": {
    "class_type": "LoadImage",
    "inputs": {
      "image": "__SKETCH__",
      "upload": "image"
    }
  },
  "3": {
    "class_type": "LoadImage",
    "inputs": {
      "image": "__STYLE_REF__",
      "upload": "image"
    }
  },
  "4": {
    "class_type": "IPAdapterModelLoader",
    "inputs": {
      "ipadapter_file": "ip-adapter-plus_sdxl_vit-h.safetensors"
    }
  },
  "5": {
    "class_type": "CLIPVisionLoader",
    "inputs": {
      "clip_name": "open_clip_model.safetensors"
    }
  },
  "6": {
    "class_type": "IPAdapterAdvanced",
    "inputs": {
      "model": ["1", 0],
      "ipadapter": ["4", 0],
      "image": ["3", 0],
      "clip_vision": ["5", 0],
      "weight": 0.85,
      "weight_type": "linear",
      "combine_embeds": "concat",
      "start_at": 0.0,
      "end_at": 1.0,
      "embeds_scaling": "V only"
    }
  },
  "7": {
    "class_type": "ControlNetLoader",
    "inputs": {
      "control_net_name": "controlnet-scribble-sdxl-1.0.safetensors"
    }
  },
  "8": {
    "class_type": "ScribblePreprocessor",
    "inputs": {
      "image": ["2", 0],
      "resolution": 1024
    }
  },
  "9": {
    "class_type": "CLIPTextEncode",
    "inputs": {
      "text": "high quality illustration, detailed linework, masterpiece, best quality",
      "clip": ["1", 1]
    }
  },
  "10": {
    "class_type": "CLIPTextEncode",
    "inputs": {
      "text": "low quality, blurry, watermark, text, bad anatomy, extra limbs",
      "clip": ["1", 1]
    }
  },
  "11": {
    "class_type": "ControlNetApplyAdvanced",
    "inputs": {
      "positive": ["9", 0],
      "negative": ["10", 0],
      "control_net": ["7", 0],
      "image": ["8", 0],
      "strength": 0.8,
      "start_percent": 0.0,
      "end_percent": 1.0
    }
  },
  "12": {
    "class_type": "KSampler",
    "inputs": {
      "model": ["6", 0],
      "positive": ["11", 0],
      "negative": ["11", 1],
      "latent_image": ["13", 0],
      "seed": 42,
      "steps": 25,
      "cfg": 7.0,
      "sampler_name": "euler",
      "scheduler": "karras",
      "denoise": 1.0
    }
  },
  "13": {
    "class_type": "EmptyLatentImage",
    "inputs": {
      "width": 1024,
      "height": 1024,
      "batch_size": 1
    }
  },
  "14": {
    "class_type": "VAEDecode",
    "inputs": {
      "samples": ["12", 0],
      "vae": ["1", 2]
    }
  },
  "15": {
    "class_type": "SaveImage",
    "inputs": {
      "images": ["14", 0],
      "filename_prefix": "craftflow_enhanced"
    }
  }
}
